{"id":2054,"date":"2021-03-24T17:25:54","date_gmt":"2021-03-24T17:25:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/?p=2054"},"modified":"2021-07-30T16:54:14","modified_gmt":"2021-07-30T16:54:14","slug":"tinh-chat-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/tinh-chat-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay\/","title":{"rendered":"Tinh ch\u1ea5t Nh\u1ee5y Hoa Ngh\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Saffron c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong khi nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y kh\u00f4 (saffron) d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng th\u00ec <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/tinh-chat-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay\/\"><b>tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> &#8211; saffron oil l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb. Qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Lifenest t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y nh\u00e9!&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00fd hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb c\u00e2y ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea5y kh\u00f4 th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng. Saffron \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh &#8220;v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ecf&#8221;, c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Saffron c\u00f3 m\u00f9i th\u01a1m nh\u1eb9 gi\u1ed1ng m\u00f9i c\u1ecf kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Iran \u0111ang l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f3 s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng saffron \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi chi\u1ebfm kho\u1ea3ng 80% th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2042\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2042\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2042 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-bao-quan.jpg\" alt=\"Tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ebf t\u1eeb nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-bao-quan.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-bao-quan-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-bao-quan-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2042\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ebf t\u1eeb nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tinh ch\u1ea5t <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/saffron\/\">saffron<\/a> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tinh nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i vitamin c\u00f9ng kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 kali, canxi, magie, vitamin A, vitamin C v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u axit d\u1ec5 bay h\u01a1i kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, do \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh d\u1ea7u saffron nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 s\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb9p. Tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap gi\u1eef g\u00ecn n\u00e9t t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a thanh xu\u00e2n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>S\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/b><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2056\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2056\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2056 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tinh-chat.jpg\" alt=\"Tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ean d\u00e2y chuy\u1ec1n kh\u00e9p k\u00edn nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tinh-chat.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tinh-chat-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tinh-chat-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2056\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ean d\u00e2y chuy\u1ec1n kh\u00e9p k\u00edn nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu ho\u1ea1ch th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng b\u00f4ng hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y m\u00e0u t\u00edm. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, m\u1ed7i c\u00e2y ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 3-4 b\u00f4ng hoa, m\u1ed7i hoa ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 nh\u1ee5y hoa. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tinh d\u1ea7u ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t, b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c nh\u1ee5y hoa ph\u1ea3i h\u00e1i b\u1eb1ng tay. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1kg nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i thu ho\u1ea1ch kho\u1ea3ng 15.000-17.000 b\u00f4ng hoa.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tinh d\u1ea7u saffron \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ebf t\u1eeb 100% s\u1ee3i saffron t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t kh\u00e9p k\u00edn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t. \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 cho ra tinh d\u1ea7u saffron ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng phu, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y m\u00e0 tinh ch\u1ea5t ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf. Tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n, ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u00e0y hay ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u00f9i h\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1c. M\u00f9i h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec?<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, <\/span><b>tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">mang \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2057\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2057\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2057 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tinh-chat-saffron.jpg\" alt=\"Tinh d\u1ea7u hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tinh-chat-saffron.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tinh-chat-saffron-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-tinh-chat-saffron-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2057\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tinh d\u1ea7u hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saffron oil gi\u00fap da tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: V\u1edbi h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy cao nh\u01b0 crocin v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i vitamin, kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba s\u1ea1m n\u00e1m. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam t\u1ed1t, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u h\u01a1n.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron gi\u00fap th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u nhanh v\u00e0o da, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y ra hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn da lu\u00f4n c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam lo\u00e9t d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nhanh ch\u00f3ng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/saffron-tri-mat-ngu\/\">hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7<\/a> t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 kinh ni\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, d\u00e2n v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, b\u00e0 n\u1ed9i tr\u1ee3,&#8230; nh\u1edd c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Crocin v\u00e0 Safranal. Nh\u1eefng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u0103ng n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 Norepinephrine, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c c\u01a1n \u0111au th\u1ea7n kinh k\u00e9o d\u00e0i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u00f3m vitamin B trong tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng xoa d\u1ecbu h\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh gi\u00fap n\u00e3o b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tr\u00ed nh\u1edb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u1ed4n \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim m\u1ea1ch: Trong tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh huy\u1ebft \u00e1p, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh tim m\u1ea1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf cholesterol, ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tim m\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, trong tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t gi\u00fap \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan v\u1ec1 m\u1eaft nh\u01b0 vi\u00eam v\u00f5ng m\u1ea1c, tho\u00e1i h\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0ng, gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00f5ng m\u1ea1c,&#8230; \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t carotenoid c\u00f3 trong saffron s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm s\u1ef1 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o v\u00f5ng m\u1ea1c, b\u1ed5 sung k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi vitamin A, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng th\u1ecb l\u1ef1c cho m\u1eaft.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 c\u00e1c ni\u00eam m\u1ea1c da \u0111\u1ea7u, gi\u00fap t\u00f3c tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eafc kh\u1ecfe tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01a1m thanh m\u00e1t v\u00e0 v\u00f4 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 th\u00e1i, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><b>C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y&nbsp;<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron kh\u00e1c nhau. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Lifenest s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eb9o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Massage c\u00f9ng tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2058\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2058\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2058 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-oil-massage.jpg\" alt=\"Massage da c\u00f9ng tinh d\u1ea7u saffron gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-oil-massage.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-oil-massage-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-oil-massage-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2058\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massage da c\u00f9ng tinh d\u1ea7u saffron gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massage nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng tinh \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y s\u1ebd k\u00edch th\u00edch l\u00e0n da v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh. T\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng sau nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, massage to\u00e0n c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng tinh d\u1ea7u saffron s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u00e1ng h\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0i gi\u1ecdt tinh nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y l\u00ean da r\u1ed3i massage nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng l\u00ean v\u00f9ng da \u0111\u00f3. Tinh d\u1ea7u s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u00e0n da, gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1eb9o v\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean da.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>G\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f9ng tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y&nbsp;<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2059\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2059\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2059 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-dau-goi.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng d\u1ea7u g\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea7u x\u1ea3 gi\u00fap t\u00f3c tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eafc kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-dau-goi.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-dau-goi-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-dau-goi-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2059\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng d\u1ea7u g\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea7u x\u1ea3 gi\u00fap t\u00f3c tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eafc kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e3y r\u1ee5ng t\u00f3c l\u00e0 do c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac t\u00f3c m\u1ecfng, y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y ra nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0i gi\u1ecdt tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng d\u1ea7u g\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea7u x\u1ea3. Sau \u0111\u00f3 massage nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng l\u00ean da \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u v\u00e0o t\u1eebng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac v\u00e0 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng nang t\u00f3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>N\u00e2ng cao s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe&nbsp;<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2016\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2016\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2016 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-nguoi-cao-tuoi.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-nguoi-cao-tuoi.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-nguoi-cao-tuoi-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/saffron-nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-nguoi-cao-tuoi-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2016\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hay h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp h\u00e3y th\u1eed pha m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i gi\u1ecdt tinh d\u1ea7u saffron c\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh d\u1ea7u saffron th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n m\u00e1u, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00ed nh\u1edb v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 s\u00e2u v\u00e0 ngon h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a ho\u1ea1<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh huy\u1ebft \u00e1p v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n c\u00f9ng tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng serotonin &#8211; \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t d\u1eabn truy\u1ec1n th\u1ea7n kinh chi ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u00e8m \u0103n, lo \u00e2u v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac. \u0110\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn calo nh\u1eb1m <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/nhuy-hoa-nghe-tay-giam-can\/\">gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n nhanh h\u01a1n<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y, <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/\">y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o<\/a> Lifenest \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb chi ti\u1ebft c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a <\/span><b>tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Hy v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tinh ch\u1ea5t saffron \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong khi nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y kh\u00f4 (saffron) d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng th\u00ec tinh ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y &#8211; saffron oil l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb. Qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Lifenest t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tinh d\u1ea7u nh\u1ee5y hoa ngh\u1ec7 t\u00e2y nh\u00e9!&nbsp; [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2060,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_seopress_robots_primary_cat":"none"},"categories":[20],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2054"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2054"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2054\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3953,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2054\/revisions\/3953"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2060"}],"wp:attachment":[